{
  "message": "feat(dashboard): add create VM modal to fleet page\n\nAdds a \"New VM\" button in the fleet header that opens a modal dialog for\ncreating new VMs. The modal includes fields for repository URL, git ref,\nname, CPUs, and memory. Submits to /api/vm/create and reloads on success.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
